{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-js","path":"/users/argocd-apps/docs/add_application.md","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Operate First"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"868d671d-adc2-5126-bafb-55cfefcefbd2","html":"<h1 id=\"adding-argocd-applications\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#adding-argocd-applications\" aria-label=\"adding argocd applications permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Adding ArgoCD Applications</h1>\n<p>This repo contains all operate-first ArgoCD <a href=\"https://argoproj.github.io/argo-cd/operator-manual/declarative-setup/#applications\">Applications</a>.</p>\n<p>Please see the use-cases below and follow the instructions that best fit your application’s needs.</p>\n<h1 id=\"pre-requisites\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#pre-requisites\" aria-label=\"pre requisites permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Pre-requisites</h1>\n<ul class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>You should have <a href=\"https://kubectl.docs.kubernetes.io/installation/kustomize/\">kustomize</a> installed</li>\n<li>You should be familiar with <a href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/manage-kubernetes-objects/kustomization/#bases-and-overlays\">kustomize ovelrays</a></li>\n<li>You should be familiar with what an <a href=\"https://argoproj.github.io/argo-cd/operator-manual/declarative-setup/#applications\">ArgoCD application</a> is.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"i-only-want-to-deploy-to-moc\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#i-only-want-to-deploy-to-moc\" aria-label=\"i only want to deploy to moc permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>I only want to Deploy to MOC</h3>\n<p>Add your ArgoCD Application to <code class=\"language-text\">overlays/moc/$PROJECT</code> where <code class=\"language-text\">$PROJECT</code> correlates with your project.\nAdd this resource to the <code class=\"language-text\">resource</code> field list in <code class=\"language-text\">overlays/moc/$PROJECT/kustomization.yaml</code>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"i-only-want-to-deploy-to-quicklab\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#i-only-want-to-deploy-to-quicklab\" aria-label=\"i only want to deploy to quicklab permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>I only want to Deploy to Quicklab</h3>\n<p>Add your ArgoCD Application to <code class=\"language-text\">overlays/quicklab/$PROJECT</code> where <code class=\"language-text\">$PROJECT</code> correlates with your project.\nAdd this resource to the <code class=\"language-text\">resource</code> field list in <code class=\"language-text\">overlays/quicklab/$PROJECT/kustomization.yaml</code>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"i-want-to-be-able-to-deploy-to-moc-and-quicklab\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#i-want-to-be-able-to-deploy-to-moc-and-quicklab\" aria-label=\"i want to be able to deploy to moc and quicklab permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>I want to be able to deploy to MOC and Quicklab</h3>\n<p>There are 2 sub use-cases here:</p>\n<h4 id=\"i-dont-use-overlays-one-set-of-manifests\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#i-dont-use-overlays-one-set-of-manifests\" aria-label=\"i dont use overlays one set of manifests permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>I don’t use overlays (one set of manifests)</h4>\n<p>Add your ArgoCD Application to <code class=\"language-text\">base/$PROJECT</code> where <code class=\"language-text\">$PROJECT</code> correlates with your project. It will be auto consumed\nby <code class=\"language-text\">moc</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">quicklab</code> overlays. The <code class=\"language-text\">path</code> should point to the path in your repo that contains the manifests.</p>\n<h4 id=\"i-use-overlays-for-moc-and-quicklab-that-inherit-from-a-base\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#i-use-overlays-for-moc-and-quicklab-that-inherit-from-a-base\" aria-label=\"i use overlays for moc and quicklab that inherit from a base permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>I use overlays for moc and quicklab that inherit from a base</h4>\n<p>The assumption here is that your manifest repository follows this structure:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">.\n├──base\n├──overlays\n│   ├── quicklab\n│   └── moc</code></pre></div>\n<p>This use case is essentially a combination of the above and requires a couple of steps:</p>\n<ol class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>Add your ArgoCD Application to <code class=\"language-text\">base/$PROJECT</code> where <code class=\"language-text\">$PROJECT</code> correlates with your project like in above. The <code class=\"language-text\">path</code>\nshould point to the path in your repo that contains the <code class=\"language-text\">base</code> folder.</li>\n<li>Add a <a href=\"https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/kustomize/blob/master/examples/inlinePatch.md#inline-patch-for-patchesstrategicmerge\">strategic patch file</a>\nto <code class=\"language-text\">overlays/moc/$PROJECT</code> that updates the <code class=\"language-text\">path</code> field to point to the <code class=\"language-text\">overlays/moc</code> folder in your repository.</li>\n<li>Add this resource to the <code class=\"language-text\">patchesStrategicMerge</code> field list in <code class=\"language-text\">overlays/moc/$PROJECT/kustomization.yaml</code>.</li>\n<li>Repeat 2) and 3) for <code class=\"language-text\">quicklab</code> but use <code class=\"language-text\">overlays/quicklab</code> instead of <code class=\"language-text\">overlays/moc</code>.</li>\n</ol>","fields":{"srcLink":"https://github.com/operate-first/argocd-apps/blob/master/docs/add_application.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"","description":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"868d671d-adc2-5126-bafb-55cfefcefbd2"}},"staticQueryHashes":["117426894","3000541721"]}